But he fights dirty.

324
00:30:30.371 --> 00:30:31.539
Like how?

325
00:30:37.628 --> 00:30:38.671
Go!

326
00:30:44.385 --> 00:30:45.594
He ruins the matches.

327
00:30:45.719 --> 00:30:48.305
He attacks until the data breaks down.

328
00:30:48.347 --> 00:30:50.391
