00:40:59.833 --> 00:41:02.335
Mrs. Tsutsui. two lunch specials!

500
00:41:02.669 --> 00:41:03.837
Okay.

501
00:41:04.671 --> 00:41:07.048
It's definitely not a publicity stunt.

502
00:41:07.174 --> 00:41:11.219
